                            <p align="center"><font color="#ff0000"
                                face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"
                                size="5"><b><font color="#0000ff">Nos
                                    stages<br>
                                    <br>
                                    "R&eacute;seaux et s&eacute;curit&eacute;"</font> </b></font></p>
                          </td>
                          <td bordercolor="#000000" ?=""
                            bgcolor="#66ffff" width="70%">
                            <p align="left"><font color="#0000ff"
                                face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"
                                size="3"><b>- WATCHGUARD Firewall Basics
                                  with Fireware - Full course - 3 jours<br>
                                  <br>
                                  - WATCHGUARD Fireware Advanced
                                  (Multi-Wan, Vlan, etc.) - 2 jours <br>
                                  <br>
                                  - WATCHGUARD Firebox X Edge and X Edge
                                  Wireless<br>
                                  - 1 jour<br>
                                  <br>
                                  - Sensibilisation &agrave; la s&eacute;curit&eacute;
                                  informatique - 2 jours <br>
                                  <br>
                                  - Comprendre les r&eacute;seaux TCP/ IP et
                                  les routeurs - </b></font><font
